Unfortunately I have not see one of these on the market in years.  Suspect I will probably have to pay a pretty penny but anxious to see what is out there.  Please email me if you have something available.  

Thanks so much!

Brian

Had two of them over the years, both long gone now. In todays market, I would suspect mid 4-figures for a lower grade example and approaching 5-figures for a higher grade one. There are a few out there so there is certainly hope.
I have one and would be open to discussing a sale.
